| $project       | \{ "\_id": 1, "teachers": 1, "score": \{ $meta: "searchScore" }, "highlights": \{ "$meta": "searchHighlights" } }If you enabled Auto Preview, MongoDB Compass displays the following documents next to the $project pipeline stage:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |```json
